  "texts": [
    "This allows us to conclude that future LLM, not only increasing in size, but also with longer training time, advanced model structures such as chain-of-thoughts [27], improved hyperparameters, larger training datasets, and detailed training on Exudyn or similar libraries, could perform much better than available models today.",
